  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Tear your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces and add them to a baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 6-7 min or until golden and crisp – these are your <strong>crispy croutons</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
