            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>reserved nectarine</strong> roughly and add it to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> wholegrain mustard </strong>with your<strong> white wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> </strong>1 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [2 1/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> sugar</strong>,<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>mustard dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
