    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomatoes </strong>roughly</p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber </strong>into quarters lengthways, then dice roughly</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove the <strong>outer leaves</strong> from the <strong>lettuce</strong> and shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
