    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>mustard dressing</strong>,<strong> torn lettuce </strong>and <strong>shredded inner core </strong>in a large bowl with the <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>diced cucumber</strong> and <strong>dried cranberries</strong> and toss until fully combined – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
