      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>nectarine wedges</strong> and cook for 1-2 min on each side, or until charred – these are your <strong>charred nectarine wedges</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
